{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/film-hit-run-diadaptasi-menjadi-game-mobile/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Film Hit &#038; Run Diadaptasi Menjadi Game Mobile","content":"\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Agate (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/agate-resmikan-kantor-baru-dan-kerja-sama-dengan-bekraf/\" target=\"_blank\">Agate</a> kembali hadir untuk berkolaborasi dengan industri perfilman Indonesia. Kali ini, Agate berkolaborasi dengan film <em>Hit &amp; Run,</em> film begenre komediâ€“laga pertama di Indonesia, untuk memproduksi sebuah <em>game</em> HTML5 berjudul serupa filmnya. <em>Game</em> HTML5 merupakan <em>game</em> yang tidak menggunakan aplikasi serta dapat diakses langsung dari <em>link</em> yang dibagikan. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54511\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-hit-run-diadaptasi-menjadi-game-mobile/attachment/02-hit-and-run-game/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/02-hit-and-run-game.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,608\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-hit-and-run-game\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/02-hit-and-run-game-300x300.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/02-hit-and-run-game.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/02-hit-and-run-game.jpg\" alt=\"Tampilan utama game Hit &amp; Run. Sumber: Agate\" class=\"wp-image-54511\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/02-hit-and-run-game.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/02-hit-and-run-game-280x280.jpg 280w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/02-hit-and-run-game-300x300.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Tampilan utama game Hit &#038; Run. Sumber: Agate</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Selain itu, <em>game</em> HTML5 buatan Agate juga mudah untuk diakses sehingga dapat memberikan kenyamanan pada pemain untuk menikmati <em>game</em> <em>Hit &amp; Run</em>. <em>Game</em> HTML5 dari Agate ini dapat menyimpan sampai 80% memori daripada <em>game </em>biasa dalam memuat halaman <em>game</em> karena ukurannya yang hanya sebesar 140kb. <em>Game</em> ini dapat di akses di <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"http://screenplay.id/gamehitnrun\" target=\"_blank\">http://screenplay.id/gamehitnrun</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54512\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-hit-run-diadaptasi-menjadi-game-mobile/attachment/03-hit-and-run-game/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/03-hit-and-run-game.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,608\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-hit-and-run-game\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/03-hit-and-run-game-300x300.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/03-hit-and-run-game.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/03-hit-and-run-game.jpg\" alt=\"Empat karakter dari filmnya bisa dimainkan. Sumber: Agate\" class=\"wp-image-54512\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/03-hit-and-run-game.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/03-hit-and-run-game-280x280.jpg 280w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/03-hit-and-run-game-300x300.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Empat karakter dari filmnya bisa dimainkan. Sumber: Agate</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Di dalam <em>game</em> <em>Hit &amp; Run,</em> para pemain dapat memilih 1 dari 4 karakter yang akan mereka mainkan. Karakter-karakter tersebut yakni Tegar yang diperankan oleh Joe Taslim, Lio yang diperankan oleh Chandra Liow, Meisa Sandriana yang diperankan oleh Tatjana Saphira, dan Jefri yang diperankan oleh Jefri Nichol. Setelah memilih karakter yang ingin dimainkan, para pemain akan diberikan tiga kesempatan untuk kalah melawan barel dan musuh. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54513\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-hit-run-diadaptasi-menjadi-game-mobile/attachment/04-hit-and-run-game/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/04-hit-and-run-game.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,608\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-hit-and-run-game\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/04-hit-and-run-game-300x300.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/04-hit-and-run-game.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/04-hit-and-run-game.jpg\" alt=\"Dapatkan skor tertinggi! Sumber: Agate\" class=\"wp-image-54513\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/04-hit-and-run-game.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/04-hit-and-run-game-280x280.jpg 280w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/04-hit-and-run-game-300x300.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Dapatkan skor tertinggi! Sumber: Agate</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Cara bermain <em>game </em>ini sangatlah sederhana. Pemain hanya perlu menggerakan karakter ke posisi sesuai jalur lawan dan barel, lalu pemain harus mengarahkan karakter untuk memukul musuh dan barel untuk mendapatkan poin. Jika pemain melewatkan barel dan musuh, maka kesempatan bermain lawan akan berkurang satu. Jika pemain sudah menghabiskan tiga kesempatan, para pemain akan diarahkan untuk menonton video <em>trailer</em> film <em>Hit &amp; Run. </em>Pemain barudapat mengakses kembali <em>game</em>-nya setelah menonton <em>trailer</em> tersebut. </p>\n\n\n\n<iframe width=\"806\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/M1bk-POU7yA\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n\n\n<p>Konten <em>game\nHit &amp; Run</em> juga dimeriahkan dengan potongan <em>soundtrack </em>dari film\nyang ditampilkan oleh <em>rapper</em> terkenal Indonesia, Saykoji. <em>Game</em>\nini telah rilis sejak 22 Mei dan sudah dimainkan lebih dari 1.500 orang&nbsp; dengan nilai perolehan tertinggi 278.620.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"73d02015-b79f-5da9-b6ec-2605735585d3"}}}